c: 2
v: 164
t: "Ndithudi! Muchilengedwe chakumwamba ndi dziko lapansi ndiponso mukasinthidwe ka usiku ndi usana, ndi m’zombo zimene zimayenda pa nyanja zitanyamula katundu wothandiza anthu, ndi mvula imene Mulungu amagwetsa kuchokera ku mitambo ndipo imaukitsa nthaka imene idali yakufa, ndi mayendedwe a nyama zosiyanasiyana zimene Iye amazimwanza pa dziko lapansi; ndiponso mphepo ndi mitambo imene imakhala pakati pa kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi, ndithudi mu zimenezi muli zizindikiro kwa anthu anzeru"